cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.DS 

This paper discusses active learning algorithms, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also introduces a new loss function and a new classifier, which are relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
